            "body": "This seems to be caused by `werkzeug`'s modification.\r\nhttps://github.com/pallets/werkzeug/commit/da9d70a33\r\n\r\n@davidism, I don't think it's appropriate to feed back these error messages to the user in non-debug mode.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/pallets/werkzeug/blob/eda35e52418fc86689320b1d27c9f740f7d0aed1/werkzeug/exceptions.py#L114-L123\r\n```phthon\r\n            def get_description(self, environ=None):\r\n                out = super(cls, self).get_description(environ=environ)\r\n\r\n                if self.args:\r\n                    out += \"<p><pre><code>{}: {}</code></pre></p>\".format(\r\n                        exception.__name__,\r\n                        escape(exception.__str__(self))\r\n                    )\r\n\r\n                return out\r\n```"
